title: Shoot the Boot - Luca Schuler
description: The third #unreasonable entry from Nine Knights comes from 17 year-old Swiss Skier Luca Schuler. Luca thought it would be super cool to take the giant wall ride to the next level by hitting the coping on the mini ramp. We agree.
